flag-gems (5.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release 5.3.0.
  * Follow the upstream build-backend switch to setuptools.build_meta:
    drop torch/pybind11/cmake/ninja from the wheel-builder stage and pin
    the version for setuptools-scm.
  * Ship the operator test and benchmark suites (flaggems_tests,
    flaggems_benchmark) now included in the upstream wheel; Suggests
    python3-pytest for running them.

